56 /* glcorearb.h is for use with OpenGL core profile implementations.
57 ** It should should be placed in the same directory as gl.h and
58 ** included as <GL/glcorearb.h>.
59 **
60 ** glcorearb.h includes only APIs in the latest OpenGL core profile
61 ** implementation together with APIs in newer ARB extensions which
62 ** can be supported by the core profile. It does not, and never will
63 ** include functionality removed from the core profile, such as
64 ** fixed-function vertex and fragment processing.
65 **
66 ** Do not #include both <GL/glcorearb.h> and either of <GL/gl.h> or
67 ** <GL/glext.h> in the same source file.
68 */
69

1483 #ifndef GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1484 /* This code block is duplicated in glxext.h, so must be protected */
1485 #define GLEXT_64_TYPES_DEFINED
1486 /* Define int32_t, int64_t, and uint64_t types for UST/MSC */
1487 /* (as used in the GL_EXT_timer_query extension). */
1488 #if defined(__STDC_VERSION__) && __STDC_VERSION__ >= 199901L
1489 #include <inttypes.h>
1490 #elif defined(__sun__) || defined(__digital__)
1491 #include <inttypes.h>
1492 #if defined(__STDC__)
1493 #if defined(__arch64__) || defined(_LP64)
1494 typedef long int int64_t;
1495 typedef unsigned long int uint64_t;
1496 #else
1497 typedef long long int int64_t;
1498 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1499 #endif /* __arch64__ */
1500 #endif /* __STDC__ */
1501 #elif defined( __VMS ) || defined(__sgi)
1502 #include <inttypes.h>
1503 #elif defined(__SCO__) || defined(__USLC__)
1504 #include <stdint.h>
1505 #elif defined(__UNIXOS2__) || defined(__SOL64__)
1506 typedef long int int32_t;
1507 typedef long long int int64_t;
1508 typedef unsigned long long int uint64_t;
1509 #elif defined(_WIN32) && defined(__GNUC__)
1510 #include <stdint.h>
1511 #elif defined(_WIN32)
1512 typedef __int32 int32_t;
1513 typedef __int64 int64_t;
1514 typedef unsigned __int64 uint64_t;
1515 #else
1516 /* Fallback if nothing above works */
1517 #include <inttypes.h>
1518 #endif
1519 #endif
